    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >That morning, I took my hand cannon and ventured into the worm caves for food—or at least, so I told the others. The real reason lay somewhere between boredom and restlessness, which made me turn to things that I was good at.<br><br>I was damned good at hunting worms.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194740/extras/f2b1d0c2fb58cf4790211c4468c54c4c.poster.avif?t=1769718121\" width=800 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194740/extras/f2b1d0c2fb58cf4790211c4468c54c4c.webm?t=1769718121\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194740/extras/f2b1d0c2fb58cf4790211c4468c54c4c.mp4?t=1769718121\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as Jack &amp; AmI, two unique characters with 40 unique skills for each.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194740/extras/f27f9399bb6daa56bf84113a67836329.poster.avif?t=1769718121\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194740/extras/f27f9399bb6daa56bf84113a67836329.webm?t=1769718121\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194740/extras/f27f9399bb6daa56bf84113a67836329.mp4?t=1769718121\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unravel the puzzle of Slither as you explore the caveback of District 4 in its unique blight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194740/extras/ba069dfdd5cf24ae5c70a86104da1f0d.poster.avif?t=1769718121\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194740/extras/ba069dfdd5cf24ae5c70a86104da1f0d.webm?t=1769718121\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194740/extras/ba069dfdd5cf24ae5c70a86104da1f0d.mp4?t=1769718121\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy the complex but intuitive tactical RPG combat and plan your actions thoroughly in accordance with your playstyle<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194740/extras/c049d073dd66881178a666cae14cb4a6.poster.avif?t=1769718121\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194740/extras/c049d073dd66881178a666cae14cb4a6.webm?t=1769718121\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194740/extras/c049d073dd66881178a666cae14cb4a6.mp4?t=1769718121\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
